keyFacts: A U.S. Customs and Border Protection TECS record for Ghislaine Maxwell was created on August 27, 2019.
The record categorizes Maxwell as a 'SUSPECT, OTHER' and applies a 'SILENT HIT' action code to her.
The 'SILENT HIT' status was set to be active from August 27, 2019, to August 27, 2020, indicating a one-year period of law enforcement monitoring for travel.
